Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
i think it's a good thing. for freshman, their first year at school will not be easy for them. so it's convenient for them to stay in the dorm and get used to the campus life without worrying about where to live. also, it's a good time they could use to make friends before they all go to different directions. in this way, the university is creating more opportunities for the students to bond.